CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1780747879
OL,3,CSuspended councillor misled party when
OL,4,Cteaming up with Greens says Tory leader
OL,6,FToday, we asked Tory leader Kemi
OL,7,FBadenoch whether this decision went
OL,8,Fagainst what she told ITV Central
OL,9,Fbefore this year's local elections,
OL,10,Fwhen she said she trusted local
OL,11,Fcouncillors to make decisions about
OL,12,Fforming coalitions.
OL,14,FShe says she hasn't changed her mind,
OL,15,F"We are open to coalition deals or
OL,16,Fagreements at the local level as long
OL,17,Fas those deals are going to deliver
OL,18,Ffor local people.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1780747879
OL,3,CSuspended councillor misled party when
OL,4,Cteaming up with Greens says Tory leader
OL,6,F"That council leader was suspended
OL,7,Fbecause he told his colleagues, as
OL,8,Fwell as the national party, something
OL,9,Fcompletely different to what he had
OL,10,Fagreed.
OL,12,F"He made a deal where he let a smaller
OL,13,Fparty take control, a party that was
OL,14,Fsmaller than the conservative group,
OL,15,Fand dishonesty is something that I
OL,16,Fwill not tolerate in the conservative
OL,17,Fgroup.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1780747879
OL,3,CSuspended councillor misled party when
OL,4,Cteaming up with Greens says Tory leader
OL,6,F"I do trust my local councillors, but
OL,7,Fwhere people show they cannot be
OL,8,Ftrusted, then I'm afraid yes, I will
OL,9,Fstep in. "
OL,11,FAdam Kent is still a councillor in
OL,12,FWythall. In response to the Tory
OL,13,Fleader, he said, "I am currently
OL,14,Funable to comment as part of the
OL,15,Fprocedure of investigation.
OL,17,F"I am very surprised that this seems
OL,18,Fto be a one-sided arrangement and that
OL,19,Fthe party can see fit to make any
OL,20,Fallegations they like, despite me not
OL,21,Fbeing able to defend myself.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1780747879
OL,3,CSuspended councillor misled party when
OL,4,Cteaming up with Greens says Tory leader
OL,6,F"I categorically deny that I've misled
OL,7,Fanybody, and I've yet to see any
OL,8,Fevidence from the party subject to the
OL,9,Fprocedures to say otherwise.
OL,11,F"My lawyers have now chased them on
OL,12,Fseveral occasions and still have not
OL,13,Fbeen provided with any evidence to
OL,14,Fjustify the claims they have made in
OL,15,Fthe media."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
